elements.title: Navy Wife (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that the 1935 film Navy Wife, starring Claire Trevor (pictured), was the first film that deals with life as part of the Navy Nurse Corps and Medical Corps of the United States Navy?

elements.title: Anna Nikulina (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that due to variable endings of the ballet Swan Lake, Bolshoi Ballet dancer Anna Nikulina has been killed in Moscow, married to the prince in Kazan, and left alone on the lake in Chelyabinsk?
